{"tid":1267580,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥生活近況2","createTime":"2019-06-30T03:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:08:56.000Z","uid":85180,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7675da2abd6a56bcb0a03903748eb52ea614884f","tid":1267580,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"阮民安孖劉翁投資近7位數 將香港熱話搬上舞台<br />\n2019年06月29日<br />\n<br />\nE-kids成員阮民安（Tommy）及劉翁擔任監製的舞台劇《夜谷賓館營業中》舉行記者會，一眾演員莊端兒、<span style=\"color: red;\">林慧韡（達哥）</span>等出席。Tommy透露今次將網絡小說作家藍橘子的原創舞台劇故事搬上舞台，<span style=\"color: red;\">投資近7位數（以百萬計）</span>。他說跟劉翁相識廿載，不過做歌手時跟對方未曾合作，反而當爸後，大家經常講湊仔經，增加多見面機會就洽談合作事宜。<span style=\"color: red;\">問劇情可有諷刺話題？</span>他說：「故事情節會將香港近期話題放上去，例如：學童自殺、醫生吸食大麻等。」劉翁則謂劇中有任性慈母角色，但尚未落實由誰演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190629_EN_%E8%8E%8A%E7%AB%AF%E5%85%924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190629_EN_%25E8%258E%258A%25E7%25AB%25AF%25E5%2585%25924.jpg&h=b366df8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊端兒話嘴戲同性感底線都看酬勞而定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190629_EN_%E8%8E%8A%E7%AB%AF%E5%85%923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190629_EN_%25E8%258E%258A%25E7%25AB%25AF%25E5%2585%25923.jpg&h=b9a3d697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莊端兒<br />\n<br />\n莊端兒以女主角身份作性感演出，她透露拍海報時以低胸衫上陣，劇中更與豪Dee有床戲。問可有親嘴戲？她說：「睇下幾多酬勞，對手豪Dee都Ok！（性感底線？）除剩條底褲同Bra，都係睇酬勞啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190629_EN_%E8%8E%8A%E7%AB%AF%E5%85%921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190629_EN_%25E8%258E%258A%25E7%25AB%25AF%25E5%2585%25921.jpg&h=fb86d1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/06/20190629_EN_%E8%8E%8A%E7%AB%AF%E5%85%922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F06%2F20190629_EN_%25E8%258E%258A%25E7%25AB%25AF%25E5%2585%25922.jpg&h=7509d609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有份演出的莊端兒預告會有牀戲，至於有多激及性感程度，她笑說：「我在劇中非常現實，要配合角色，向錢看。（無底線？）可以除剩底褲，kiss都是看能給多少錢。」<br />\n莊端兒話嘴戲同性感底線都看酬勞而定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kVGSpfA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVGSpfA.gif&h=5c34654d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/30i112e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30i112e.gif&h=3c328232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/LfPVSfd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfPVSfd.gif&h=efcf26aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc1af6239bde5b56dae8de623530c01995d72a97","tid":1267580,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afcceb4450907ac49235689837a2414220511b3","tid":1267580,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a1bf8a98a801a9aca376ecf22b3a5e46809f08","tid":1267580,"uid":191815,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"香港熱話不包括台灣殺人案、送中、反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm